Required Repos - Suggested in initial planning on 8th August 2025

| Repo Name                          | Purpose                                               |
|-----------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------|
| `cognito-learning-hub`            | 🔧 Main app (frontend + backend)                      |
| `assignments-library`             | 📘 JSON/YAML structured assignments                   |
| `blockly-engine`                  | ⚙️ Custom Blockly config, blocks, converters          |
| `hub-docs`                        | 📚 Docs for devs, educators, contributors             |
| `student-dashboard-ui` (optional) | 🎓 Separate frontend for student-only views           |
| `plugins/roblox-sprint`           | 🕹️ Add-on scripts or Roblox snippets                 |
| `infra-docker`                    | 🐳 Dev stack config, NGINX proxy, backups, deployment |
| `demo-content`                    | 🎯 Sample lessons for showcase/testing                |
| `cognito-utils`                   | 🔩 Internal helpers, conversion scripts, etc.         |
